Package: euphoria
Title: ggplot2 Themes and Color Palette Inspired by HBO's Euphoria
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sam", "Acuna", email = "samruthacuna@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a ggplot2 theme and color palette inspired by the 
    visual aesthetic of HBO's television show Euphoria. Features deep purple-black 
    backgrounds, neon orchid accents, and character-named color palettes 
    for use in data visualizations.
